  "commentary": "With SPX at 6780.52 sitting between the massive +9405.6M gamma wall at 6800 and the +7080.9M wall at 6775, dealers are in full stabilization mode, actively selling this bounce toward 6800 resistance while the PIN regime suggests they'll aggressively buy any dips back toward 6750-6775 support. The wall_break detection combined with the -1.7% 1-min move followed by +2.8% 5-min recovery shows classic dealer hedge flow—they're capping upside momentum and creating a magnetic pull toward the 6775-6785 zone. Key levels: dealers turn heavy sellers above 6800, while 6750 becomes a strong buy zone with escalating support down to the GEX flip at 6678.\n\nBottom line: expect price to get pinned between 6775-6800 with dealers capping moves in both directions.",
